GoBike System Data Insights¶

by Tarek Fayyad¶

Investigation Overview¶

In this investigation, I wanted to look at GoBike rental duration time and its interesting relationships with users age, users gender, users sbuscribtion type, distance between station, weekday and daily hours.

Dataset Overview¶

Bay Wheels is a regional public bicycle sharing system in California's San Francisco Bay Area.
This data set includes information about Ford GoBike individual ride for 183,412 trips.
Each trip information includes: duration in seconds, start_time, end_time, start_station_id, start_station_name, start_station_latitude, start_station_longitude, end_station_id, end_station_name, end_station_latitude, end_station_longitude, bike_id user_type, member_birth_year, member_gender and bike_share_for_all_trip.

Distribution of GoBike Rental Duration¶

  • The rental duration averge between 1 to 35 minutes with averge of 9.7 minutes.
  • Users most frequent duration is 5.4 minutes.
  • 75% of duration range is about 12.7 minutes.

Distribution of GoBike Rental Duration Vs Gender¶

  • Gender Distribution
    • Male proportion is about three times female proportion, with respectively 74.6%,and 23.4%.
    • Other proportion is 2%.
  • The most frequent male trip duration is from 4.6 to 5.4 minutes.
  • The most frequent female trip duration is from 4.8 to 6.4 minutes.
  • The most frequent other trip duration is from 4.4 to 7 minutes.
  • The quantities of male is higher than female and other in using GoBike.

Distribution of GoBike Rental Duration Vs Age¶

  • Age Distribution
    • Users age ranging from 18 to 69 years old with averge of 34 years old.
  • Users with age of 31 years old are the most frequent users of GoBike with averge duration of 10 minutes.
  • Users with age range from 24 to 33 years old are the most frequent users of GoBike with averge duration of 9.8 minutes.
  • Users with age range from 55 to 69 years old are the least frequent users of Gobike.
  • Users with 18 years old are rarely using GoBike.

Distribution of GoBike Rental Duration Vs Distance between station¶

  • Distance in meters Distribution
    • The distance range from 0 to 12410 meters with averge of 1686 meters.
    • Most of users make trip that range from 900 to 1500 meters.
    • There is a lot of distrubition at 0 distance which mean users return to start station
  • At 0 distance, duration range from 1 to 35 minutes with average duration of 12.7 minutes.
  • At distance > 0, duration range from 1 to 35 minutes with average of 9.7 minutes.

Distribution of GoBike Rental Duration Vs Users Types¶

  • Users Types Distribution
    • The subscriber proportion is about 10 times customer proportion, with respectively 90.5% and 9.5%.
  • Customer user type have averge trip duration of 13.5 minutes.
  • Subscribe user type have averge trip duration of 9.4 minutes.

GoBike Rental Duration Vs Age & Distance¶

As distance between station increase , rental duration increase.
There is no correlation between age and duration.
There is no correlation between age and distance.

GoBike Rental Duration Vs User type & Start Hour¶

GoBike usage for Subscriber is almost the same regarding daily hour.
GoBike usage for customer differ according hour. The most usage is at 3,4,11,13,14 o'clock

GoBike Rental Duration Vs User type & Start Hour¶

Trip duration for Subscriber is almost the same regarding week day.
Trip duration for customer is higher than subscriber especially in Saturday and Sunday.
